# GiroCode Generator — Design System Rules

Du arbeitest am Redesign von girocodegenerator.com. 
Halte dich bei JEDER Seite und Komponente exakt an dieses Design-System.

---

## SCHRIFT
- Font: Manrope (Google Fonts, weights 400 500 600 700 800)
- Immer antialiased: -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased
- Headlines: weight 800, letter-spacing -0.04em, line-height 1.05
- Body: weight 500, line-height 1.65–1.7
- Labels (uppercase): weight 700, letter-spacing 0.08em, font-size 10–11px
- NIEMALS: Inter, Roboto, Arial oder andere Fonts

## FARBEN
```
Primär:        #22c55e   (Buttons, Akzente, Links)
Primär Hover:  #16a34a
Primär Tint:   #f0fdf4   (Hero-BG, Hover-Flächen)
Primär Light:  #dcfce7   (Badges, Chips)

Blau Akzent:   #3b82f6   (Sekundäre Aktionen, SVG-Download)
Blau Hover:    #2563eb
Blau Tint:     #eff6ff

Text:          #0f172a   (Headlines, wichtiger Text)
Text-2:        #334155   (Normaler Text)
Text-3:        #64748b   (Beschreibungen, Labels)
Text-4:        #94a3b8   (Placeholder, Captions)

Rahmen:        #e2e8f0
Surface:       #f8fafc   (Input-BG, Karten-BG)
Weiß:          #ffffff
```

## RADIEN
- Karten / große Container: 22px
- Inputs / kleinere Elemente: 11px  
- Buttons: 11–13px
- Badges / Pills: 100px
- Logo SVG: rx="44"

## SCHATTEN
- Karte: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04), 0 20px 56px rgba(0,0,0,.09)
- Button Hover (grün): 0 4px 14px rgba(34,197,94,.3)
- Button Hover (blau): 0 4px 14px rgba(59,130,246,.3)

---

## NAVIGATION (alle Seiten gleich)
- Sticky, top 0, z-index 100
- Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88) + backdrop-filter: blur(20px)
- Border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0
- Höhe: 64px, max-width: 1200px, padding: 0 28px
- Logo: Pixel-G SVG (36px) + Wortmarke "GiroCode" (Giro=weight 500, Code=weight 800)
- Nav-Links: 14px weight 600, color #64748b
  - Hover: background #f8fafc, color #0f172a, border-radius 9px
- CTA: "QR-Code erstellen", background #22c55e, Hover #16a34a

## HERO (Startseite)
- Background: linear-gradient(180deg, #edfaf3 0%, #ffffff 58%)
- 2-Spalten Grid (5fr 7fr), gap 72px, max-width 1200px
- Links: Badge + H1 + Beschreibung + Trust-Checks
- Rechts: Generator-Card

## SONSTIGE SEITEN (Wissen, Blog, Über uns, etc.)
- Weißer Hintergrund (#ffffff)
- Hero-Bereich: dezenter grüner Gradient (wie Startseite aber schlanker: padding 48px)
- Page-Title: H1, 800, max-width 680px
- Content-Bereich: max-width 760px (Text) oder 1200px (Grid-Layouts)
- Immer gleiche Navigation und Footer

---

## BUTTONS
```css
/* Primär (grün) */
background: #22c55e; color: white; border: none;
border-radius: 11px; padding: 9px 18px;
font: 700 13px Manrope; cursor: pointer;
transition: all .2s;
/* Hover: */ background: #16a34a; transform: translateY(-1px); 
box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(34,197,94,.3);

/* Sekundär (outline) */
background: white; color: #334155;
border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 11px;
/* Hover: */ border-color: #22c55e; color: #16a34a; background: #f0fdf4;
```

## INPUTS
```css
background: #f8fafc; border: 1.5px solid transparent;
border-radius: 11px; padding: 10px 13px;
font: 500 14px Manrope; color: #0f172a;
outline: none; transition: all .18s;
/* Hover: */ background: #eef1f6;
/* Focus: */ background: white; border-color: #22c55e; 
             box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(34,197,94,.14);
```

## KARTEN
```css
background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
border-radius: 22px;
box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04), 0 20px 56px rgba(0,0,0,.09);
```

## BADGES / CHIPS
```css
display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
background: #dcfce7; color: #16a34a;
font: 700 11.5px Manrope; letter-spacing: .04em;
padding: 5px 13px 5px 8px; border-radius: 100px;
```

---

